import {React, useState, any} from 'react'; import { useLocation } from 'react-router-dom'; // Assuming you are using React Router for navigation import DataGrid from "react-data-grid"; import 'react-data-grid/lib/styles.css'; function InputReview() { const location = useLocation(); const dataToPass = location.state; const { dataRows, dataColumnHeaders, openYear, closeYear, CalClosureYear, WasteDesignCapacity, gas1, gas2, gas3, gas4, MethaneGenerationRate, PotentialMethanGenCap, NMOCConcentration, MethaneContent, UnitType, UnitType2, } = dataToPass; return (
